Package: read.sql
Title: Reads .SQL Files And Execute Them
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Vikram",
      family = "Rawat",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "vikram_singh_rawat@outlook.com"
    )
Description: Writing your SQL into character strings is never a good idea. 
  This package helps you write SQL in sql files and read them at your will and 
  execute them directly with a db. It also helps run migration scripts on a SQL DB.
